Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:02.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.85,0:00:06.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna was good friends with \NNatsu since they were children,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.26,0:00:08.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but during one incident, it \Nwas thought that she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.82,0:00:12.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We eventually overcame our \Nsadness and somehow moved on...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.61,0:00:15.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But then we were reunited \Nwith Lisanna in Edolas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:19.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And moreover, she was really {\i1}our{\i0} Lisanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:53.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu and the others were tackling \Nthe S Class Wizard Advancement Exam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.88,0:01:59.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,when the powerful Dark Guild, Grimoire \NHeart, appeared before them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:01.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,While the Fairy Tail wizards \Nwere fighting a desperate battle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.01,0:02:03.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,against the Lost Magic-wielding \NSeven Kin of Purgatory,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.60,0:02:06.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Makarov was defeated by Master Hades.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:11.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will {\i1}never{\i0} forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.39,0:02:19.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate the power... of family!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.47,0:02:25.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, Natsu beat the God \NSlayer, Zancrow. However...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.15,0:02:30.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The World of Great Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:41.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:47.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Some wannabe dragon hunter... beat me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.86,0:02:52.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the enemy's magic power, \Nhe emptied out his own magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.85,0:02:56.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And he created a new vessel which lets \Nhim eat flames he couldn't eat before!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.76,0:02:59.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What manner of man is he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:04.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to give him a good \Nscolding for this later...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:05.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.26,0:03:09.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.74,0:03:14.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know there are times when \Nyou have to fall back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.84,0:03:17.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gildarts taught me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.21,0:03:22.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But this ain't one of those times.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:28.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,These bastards chose Fairy \NTail as their enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:31.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So we have to make them realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:33.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...the power of our guild, \Nwith all its heart and soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:39.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:41.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gr-Gr...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:44.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.00,0:04:00.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The power of family?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.41,0:04:02.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were going to show that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:05.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira-nee! Use Satan Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:07.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Satan Soul?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.16,0:04:10.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not magic I can use repeatedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:12.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sisters?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:17.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail's Fairy Sisters...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:19.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.75,0:04:23.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the Demon Mirajane?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:25.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:27.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When Mira-nee gets serious, \Nshe's mega-strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.66,0:04:33.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Well, I would like to \Nhave a bout with a serious demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.95,0:04:38.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You can't take this seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.99,0:04:41.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,My magic is more than \Nenough to take you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:42.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Lisanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.40,0:04:44.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.62,0:04:49.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This man... is extremely strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.39,0:04:58.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I would really rather not do this, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.32,0:05:10.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:11.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisanna!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:15.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In three minutes, that will explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:19.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it. I wouldn't put any more \Npressure on it if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.83,0:05:23.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to set her free, \Nyou'll have to defeat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.95,0:05:28.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't... get free!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:30.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You fiend!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.40,0:05:35.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything in order \Nto fight that demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:43.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:47.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't feel like my magic \Npower will last long...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.13,0:05:51.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I don't have a choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:54.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is it! This sensation!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.87,0:05:57.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.71,0:06:05.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.92,0:06:09.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me! Just focus!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.81,0:06:17.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Chain Burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.45,0:06:42.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.50,0:06:47.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let Lisanna go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.84,0:06:51.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you'd be strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.43,0:06:59.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't felt this high in a long time!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:20.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you looking at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:22.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Burst Claw!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.02,0:07:30.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:35.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Evil Explosion!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.26,0:08:06.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew this would be good...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:10.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have more fun, Mirajane!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.15,0:08:14.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No good... He's too strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:21.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If my magic power wasn't depleted...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.73,0:08:30.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.96,0:08:32.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.41,0:08:40.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Pointless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.47,0:08:43.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to stop the \Ncountdown is by beating me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.01,0:08:46.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! There's no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.85,0:08:49.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me your true strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:50.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.99,0:08:57.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's frustrating, but I don't have enough \Nmagic power left to take him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:02.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, that's impossible for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.10,0:09:06.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira-nee...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.77,0:09:13.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I have faith...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.82,0:09:20.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have faith that someone \Nin the guild can beat him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:25.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you... saying, Mira-nee?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.25,0:09:33.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm... giving up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:38.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...but you don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:48.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you die again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:34.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira... nee...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.95,0:10:39.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.13,0:10:43.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.82,0:10:46.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.76,0:10:51.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira-nee!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:11:02.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mira-nee!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:20.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The path to Zeref...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.04,0:11:21.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...has been a long one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.35,0:11:24.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Too long for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.75,0:11:31.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But today, finally, my dream will come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:37.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I have Zeref in my hands, I'll be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.84,0:11:40.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.55,0:11:43.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:51.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... You people are \Nthe "seeds of conflict".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.50,0:11:55.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.77,0:12:01.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...that you've angered me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:29.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Wendy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.14,0:12:35.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. But why won't my \Nhealing magic work on these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:39.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the Master's \Nwounds are too deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:42.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With these injuries, no matter \Nhow much Sky Magic you use...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.07,0:12:43.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What about Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.55,0:12:45.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why it doesn't work on Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:49.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing I can think of is that \Nsomething is blocking the treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:53.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu... Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.19,0:13:03.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wendy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.86,0:13:05.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.02,0:13:11.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You found us...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.61,0:13:13.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:16.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry... about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:21.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care... of Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:25.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I promise! I promise \Nthat I'll do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:29.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise that I'll help you both!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.77,0:13:32.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu's... scarf...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.94,0:13:38.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you put it back... to the way it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.80,0:13:40.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,His scarf?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.12,0:13:47.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The malevolence that stains his scarf... \Nis impeding Natsu's recovery...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.20,0:13:49.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:54.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Natsu's scarf become \Nblack in the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.15,0:13:59.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That creepy guy with black hair \NI was telling you about did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.97,0:14:01.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.29,0:14:07.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...Zeref, the man Grimoire \NHeart is looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.78,0:14:13.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:18.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,After all that searching, here you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:22.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...right in front of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:27.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You people want my power?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:35.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We desire your entire existence, Lord Zeref.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.66,0:14:47.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no intention of \Ndoing anything in this age.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.23,0:14:52.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see strife or anyone die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:58.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Cease your attacks upon this \Nisland and leave at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.48,0:15:05.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't want to see strife or anyone die?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:10.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Though he's conscious, he \Ndoesn't know who he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.73,0:15:12.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Zeref?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.68,0:15:16.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in a state of "slumber"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:21.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:43.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that monster?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:45.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look who's talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:49.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my Sacred Guardian \NBeast, Thunderclap Belcusas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.42,0:15:55.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thunderclap Belcusas...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.40,0:15:57.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's even got two names?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.61,0:16:02.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The encounter between demon and \Nangel is unavoidable destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.65,0:16:04.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about angels or demons,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.71,0:16:07.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you're a Man, \Nfight me fair and square!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:11.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Belcusas, fight them fair and square.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.12,0:16:14.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I meant you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.20,0:16:18.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Machine Gun! Leprechaun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:25.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It has no effect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.10,0:16:30.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Take Over, Beast Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:34.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:36.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All you have to do is turn \Nhim to stone, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.70,0:16:38.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That only works on humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.95,0:16:42.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! I meant the boss! That man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.51,0:16:44.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't! He's wearing glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:46.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez! You're utterly useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.13,0:16:48.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you wanna be turned to stone first?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.10,0:16:50.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When two people who love each \Nother disagree, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:52.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't love each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:57.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You stop that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.33,0:16:58.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Evergreen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:17:00.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen through to the \Ntrue nature of his magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:03.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as Lucy, Summoning Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:06.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And the weakness of those who \Nuse Summoning Magic is clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:10.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their own body is weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.44,0:17:14.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:18.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the King of the Underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:22.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This arm is an ebony sword \Nthat cuts through everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:26.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Scatter across the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:32.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Evergreen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:44.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is that magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.24,0:17:49.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I could explain it to trash, but it \Nwould be difficult to comprehend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.85,0:17:51.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For trash...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:52.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.55,0:17:55.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's magic that has gotten too close \Nto the abyss of the magic path.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.95,0:18:00.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And because of that, this magic \Nhas a powerful side effect...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:04.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, what a catastrophic fate...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:12.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But when we get our hands on Zeref,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:17.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,that catastrophe will be over and \Nan age of new magic will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:19.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one from before...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:32.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Zeref?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.93,0:18:36.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The legendary black magic wizard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:37.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That man was him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.79,0:18:43.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean... Zeref is on this island right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.86,0:18:47.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The World of Great Magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:52.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The World of Great Magic?! What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.14,0:18:56.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A world of magic governed \Nby chaos and darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:18:59.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What {\i1}is{\i0} that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.03,0:19:04.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a place where those \Nwithout magic cannot live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.51,0:19:07.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or even if they can, it's a living hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.70,0:19:13.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds wonderful, doesn't \Nit?! A world just for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.99,0:19:17.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Garbage who can't use \Nmagic won't exist there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.34,0:19:20.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When Zeref becomes the king of this world...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:23.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...the World of Great Magic will be complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:27.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those without magic power \Nwill all cease to exist!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:29.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a paradise for wizards only!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:31.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this age!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.64,0:19:34.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting forever!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:36.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I don't believe it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.80,0:19:41.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It... It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.38,0:19:46.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.26,0:19:55.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.81,0:19:57.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I'll be next...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.95,0:20:02.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But getting injured to some extent
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:04.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,is to be expected in the \Ncourse of catching Zeref.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.03,0:20:08.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lost Magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.46,0:20:09.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Ark!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:25.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll manipulate the time of those \Nphysical objects and capture Lord Zeref!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.05,0:20:31.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:33.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.45,0:20:37.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Predator of Death...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.76,0:21:19.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Ark!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.35,0:21:25.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What {\i1}are{\i0} you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:29.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Luminous Nimitz!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.20,0:21:48.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Legendary wizard or not, when \Nyour true self is sleeping,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.56,0:21:50.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you're no match for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.78,0:21:56.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make light of the leader \Nof the Seven Kin of Purgatory!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.01,0:22:03.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it'll be okay, Lord Zeref...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.04,0:22:06.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...for we possess the key to awaken you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.23,0:22:09.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.47,0:22:15.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I got him...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.70,0:22:23.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have Zeref!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.45,0:23:58.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're scattered all over the island, \Nbut I hope everyone's okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.90,0:24:00.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Erza and Gray are fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.59,0:24:02.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And Lucy is tough when it \Ncomes down to the crunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.80,0:24:05.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about Elfman.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.03,0:24:07.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he screws up during critical moments...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.99,0:24:10.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm anxious about him being \Npartners with Evergreen, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.87,0:24:13.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone from the Raijinshuu \Nhas eccentric personalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.13,0:24:16.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: "Ark of Embodiment".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.86,0:24:19.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you never know. Two oddballs \Nmight actually work well together...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.93,0:24:21.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They llllllike each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.10,0:24:23.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I haven't heard that in a while!
